OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772798582
OL,3,CWoodland Trust counting cost of
OL,4,C'disgusting' cannabis farm waste dump
OL,6,FMore than four tonnes of cannabis farm
OL,7,Fwaste has been dumped across an
OL,8,Fancient woodland in Sussex.
OL,10,FAccording to conservation charity the
OL,11,FWoodland Trust, the waste had been
OL,12,Fflytipped at Brede High Woods near
OL,13,FHastings at some point over the last
OL,14,F12 months.
OL,16,FIt says staff and the local community
OL,17,Fhave reported and recovered multiple
OL,18,Fblack bags of soil waste, propagation
OL,19,Fkits, tubing and equipment at the site
OL,20,Fat Cripps Corner, with a further 20
OL,21,Fbags awaiting removal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
