PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772798582
OL,3,CWoodland Trust counting cost of
OL,4,C'disgusting' cannabis farm waste dump
OL,6,FHelen Osorio, site manager at Brede
OL,7,FHigh Woods, said the financial and
OL,8,Fenvironmental costs are substantial.
OL,10,F"The scale of cannabis farm waste and
OL,11,Fanti-social behaviour we're dealing
OL,12,Fwith is disgusting and relentless.
OL,14,F"It's expensive, environmentally
OL,15,Fdamaging and deeply frustrating for
OL,16,Fstaff and visitors."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
