OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772798582
OL,3,CWoodland Trust counting cost of
OL,4,C'disgusting' cannabis farm waste dump
OL,6,FMs Osorio added: "We're asking local
OL,7,Fpeople to be vigilant, report anything
OL,8,Fsuspicious to the police, and help us
OL,9,Fprotect Brede High Woods from this
OL,10,Fongoing criminal activity."
OL,12,FAs the fly tipping is on Woodland
OL,13,FTrust land, it falls to them to clean
OL,14,Fit up.
OL,16,FThe Woodland Trust says that similar
OL,17,Fincidents across the South East have
OL,18,Fcost them around #15,000 in clean up
OL,19,Fcosts over the last year alone.
OL,26,@rD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
