PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772798582
OL,3,CWoodland Trust counting cost of
OL,4,C'disgusting' cannabis farm waste dump
OL,6,FIn relation to the waste dumping,
OL,7,FSussex Police say it is their
OL,8,Fresponsibility if this type of dumping
OL,9,Fis active.
OL,11,FITV News Meridian has approached
OL,12,FRother District Council to ask if
OL,13,Fthey're conducting an investigation
OL,14,Finto the dumping at Brede High Woods.
OL,16,FIt's not just Sussex that's impacted
OL,17,Fby fly tipping, Kent is affected too,
OL,18,Fwith the site at Bluebell Hill near
OL,19,FMaidstone a particular hotspot.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
