FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772798582
OL,3,CWoodland Trust counting cost of
OL,4,C'disgusting' cannabis farm waste dump
OL,6,FTalking about the waste that's dumped,
OL,7,FGeorge Kirby from Kent Friends of the
OL,8,FTrees said: "We don't know what's in
OL,9,Fthe rubbish. so it could be any amount
OL,10,Fof poison, stuff that just generally
OL,11,Fdoesn't do any good to the soil, to
OL,12,Fthe environment under the soil.
OL,14,F"So basically we'd be killing wildlife
OL,15,Fas well as potentially the trees.
OL,17,F"The people that flytip, and
OL,18,Fpotentially damage or endanger the
OL,19,Fwoodlands, should be responsible for
OL,20,Fthe cost of taking away that rubbish."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
