OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772798582
OL,3,CWoodland Trust counting cost of
OL,4,C'disgusting' cannabis farm waste dump
OL,6,FIan Rickards from the Kent Wildlife
OL,7,FTrust says that avenues for recovering
OL,8,Fclean-up costs are limited.
OL,10,F"The reality is that all those costs
OL,11,Fare lost. It's just money out and
OL,12,Fnothing back in again."
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, at the moment it's the
OL,15,Flandowner whose responsibility it is,
OL,16,Fwhich seems to be about as unjust as
OL,17,Fyou can get."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
